_104_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72641,"position":12,"arabic":"جِئْنَا","translation":"আমরা আসবো","audioUrl":"wbw/017_104_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72642,"position":13,"arabic":"بِكُمْ","translation":"নিয়ে তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_104_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72643,"position":14,"arabic":"لَفِيفًۭا","translation":"সমবেত করে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/017_104_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":72644,"position":15,"arabic":"١٠٤","translation":"(১০৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]}]}